## Query Builder
NovaPlatform provides a fluent query builder:

```typescript
import { db } from '@nova/orm';

// Simple queries
const users = await db('users').where('active', true).orderBy('name').limit(10);

// Complex queries
const result = await db('orders')
  .join('users', 'orders.user_id', 'users.id')
  .where('orders.total', '>', 100)
  .whereNotNull('orders.shipped_at')
  .select('users.name', 'orders.total', 'orders.shipped_at')
  .groupBy('users.name')
  .having('SUM(orders.total)', '>', 500);
```

## Queue System
Background job processing:

```typescript
import { queue } from '@nova/core';

// Define a job
queue.define('send-email', async (job) => {
  await EmailService.send(job.data.to, job.data.subject, job.data.body);
});

// Enqueue a job
await queue.add('send-email', {
  to: 'alice@example.com',
  subject: 'Welcome!',
  body: 'Thanks for signing up.',
});

// Schedule recurring jobs
queue.schedule('cleanup-expired-sessions', '0 */6 * * *'); // Every 6 hours
```

